{"tid":1234212,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"再唔改變佔領方式，只會係重覆犯錯","createTime":"2019-06-17T01:09:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-17T02:41:54.000Z","uid":230146,"like":45,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"33b2f6eee5f99587ad8f9e6d39aef04994151741","tid":1234212,"uid":230146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T01:09:43.000Z","msg":"呢一個星期動員得太多啦，<br />\n市民已經出現疲態跡象，<br />\n而半夜又已經出現勇武vs和理非既對立現象，<br />\n好怕長期佔領落去，<br />\n只會加深矛盾，造成分裂，<br />\n政府同差佬亦改變左態度同手法，<br />\n用溫和方式勸說，並且不理會示威者，<br />\n咁樣長期落去，又會失敗<br />\n<br />\n究竟何去何從，希望各位深思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b5f388209723d3ebbd23fba96a3637bf2fcfc9e","tid":1234212,"uid":45046,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T01:10:18.000Z","msg":"唔想變雨傘2.0嘅入一入黎<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1234083\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1234083</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n加油香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70edc857f227a51f7db5077649b6394648359d60","tid":1234212,"uid":230146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T01:10:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f15dba1755315fc6690e40f5af184a08d635a48d","tid":1234212,"uid":230146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T01:12:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6ec03c3b03de257565d2779ead351f271622139","tid":1234212,"uid":143210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T01:13:29.000Z","msg":"失敗主義不是無為的理由<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1234103\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1234103</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n希望經過今次大家學識抱打不平，友善照舊，有錯就要講！<br />\n<br />\n分化輿論要由我地親手阻止<br />\n<br />\n戰場唔止熱門仲有係最新<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n加油我地要説服全香港！"},{"pid":"de7d3b8ed5ba97ba5428d97cdf03872aa4cb107d","tid":1234212,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T01:13:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c9a55bfcfee1c376f2ce8816ccf59c93e496972a","tid":1234212,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T01:14:40.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"fb9ed112651dc2822aa0c1103ac0bc1bf163757b","tid":1234212,"uid":6211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T01:14:40.000Z","msg":"佔街太易比人清"},{"pid":"db1a4f347c9e7ad26c2ad35b3fd5f13ff9255a42","tid":1234212,"uid":230146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb9ed112651dc2822aa0c1103ac0bc1bf163757b","tid":1234212,"uid":6211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T01:14:40.000Z","msg":"佔街太易比人清"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T01:18:27.000Z","msg":"同埋一來個議題半冇左，<br />\n二來警察冇太大動作，<br />\n佔來唔知為咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2acaed32a6465ec3d0644e4bb1a319057a5f8092","tid":1234212,"uid":72480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T01:31:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"de541b1bd1c6f51d5068b873739dea37a3fcda0a","tid":1234212,"uid":183270,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T01:48:08.000Z","msg":"勇武嘅各位一定要知道自己佔路嘅目的係咩<br />\n我眼見好多義士被200萬呢個數字迷惑咗<br />\n一定要知道，世界任何一場運動，大多數人其實都係和理非<br />\n而每一場運動，所做嘅行動都係代表一個整體<br />\n我知，我明大家所講嘅兄弟爬山，各有各做<br />\n所以我打字之前我都掙扎咗幾次<br />\n但我都係想你哋明白而家好多人嘅提議都唔係割緊蓆<br />\n而係真心想你哋嘅行動可以帶嚟更有意義嘅影響<br />\n呢一刻佔路你想達到咩目的？訴諸到邊個訴求？<br />\n其實我諗你知我知，其實除咗表達民眾不徹不散嘅聲音尚未消失之外<br />\n其實政府都唔會進一步回應啲咩<br />\n要不徹不散，除咗佔路之外，野餐團、禮賓府、大使館請願都一樣<br />\n咁何必失去民意嘅授權？<br />\n我諗金鐘嘅各位要好好衡量一下"},{"pid":"cee66e382482499aba5f07ee49161d2eb6dafe1d","tid":1234212,"uid":183270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T01:52:56.000Z","msg":"香港人最大嘅力量唔單純係勇武<br />\n而係隨時調動到過百萬人走出嚟<br />\n抗爭並不局限於馬路吖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"874ed2b6859e93280b0cda7822fab3900c1764e1","tid":1234212,"uid":171574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T01:54:24.000Z","msg":"希望大家會從長計議、包圍禮賓府又好乜都好，一影響民生d人就會反，咪撚再佔路<br />\n<br />\n利申：同左堆琴日有去遊行既中年同事傾計，佢地都對佔路極反感"},{"pid":"73a89c3a3b9627af9a725109d4f906de9cc0884f","tid":1234212,"uid":26708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T01:54:38.000Z","msg":"同意"},{"pid":"94c979f70e9584c1f1ca36aa74bef70b328999cf","tid":1234212,"uid":9342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T01:55:03.000Z","msg":"同意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebefef5ff83208c7531293a61b0ae2bdb25acdd1","tid":1234212,"uid":230146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T02:34:36.000Z","msg":"希望有識之士帶領大家走出困局<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"987c4676c482a3459960a1b05c9590c104bda901","tid":1234212,"uid":8290,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T02:35:23.000Z","msg":"記住係長期戰，烈士既死唔係換取一日200萬人就算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢佔旺時期已經企出黎抗爭<br />\n佢一定想大家學佢咁堅持 而唔係出黎行一日就算<br />\n大家唯有多啲關心政治 堅持到中共交返個香港俾我地<br />\n咁先對得住佢"},{"pid":"d0add944966d08cf9200415829b1277d46d8eaf6","tid":1234212,"uid":263161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T02:36:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9145f9b084ca5dd99f20059db002c9f01d9796e6","tid":1234212,"uid":230146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d0add944966d08cf9200415829b1277d46d8eaf6","tid":1234212,"uid":263161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"33b2f6eee5f99587ad8f9e6d39aef04994151741","tid":1234212,"uid":230146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T01:09:43.000Z","msg":"呢一個星期動員得太多啦，<br />\n市民已經出現疲態跡象，<br />\n而半夜又已經出現勇武vs和理非既對立現象，<br />\n好怕長期佔領落去，<br />\n只會加深矛盾，造成分裂，<br />\n政府同差佬亦改變左態度同手法，<br />\n用溫和方式勸說，並且不理會示威者，<br />\n咁樣長期落去，又會失敗<br />\n<br />\n究竟何去何從，希望各位深思<img src=\"/assets/f